## OUTPUT SCHEMA

```json
[
  {
    "subject": "<canonical entity name or literal>",
    "predicate": "<present-tense verb, lowercase>",
    "object": "<canonical entity name or literal value>",
    "confidence": 0.95,
    "subject_type": "entity" | "literal",
    "object_type": "entity" | "literal"
  }
]
```

- **subject_type** and **object_type** are "entity" when the value is a
  named node in the graph, "literal" when it's an attribute/description.
- If no new facts can be added to the graph, output `[]`.

